Fixed bug: No Activity Report is presented to Users, like Anonymous, that are not permitted to ellaborate an up-to-date Activity Report, when the existing Activity Report is obsolete or none exists.
Addition: In the translations page, when the user requests to hide the left-side column with symbols, then rows with the symbol are added on top of each translation.


